sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Usuario
    participant C as Cliente React
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant S as Community Service
    participant K as Keycloak
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis

    U->>C: 1. Abre sección Comunidad / Feed
    
    C->>G: 2. GET /community/personalized?limit=10
    Note over C,G: Authorization: Bearer {token}
    
    G->>S: 3. Proxy → /community/personalized
    
    S->>K: 4. Introspect token
    K-->>S: userInfo (postgresId)
    
    alt Token inválido
        S-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
        C-->>U: Redirigir a login
    else Token válido
    
        S->>R: 5. GET community:personalized:feed:{userId}
        
        alt Cache HIT
            R-->>S: posts (JSON)
            S-->>C: 200 OK (posts)
            C-->>U: Mostrar feed
        else Cache MISS
        
            S->>P: 6. SELECT * FROM get_personalized_feed({userId}, 10)
            Note over S,P: Función PL/pgSQL optimizada:
            Note over S,P: - Posts de usuarios seguidos (prioridad +10)
            Note over S,P: - Likes +1.5, comentarios +2.0
            Note over S,P: - Tags coincidentes +3.0
            Note over S,P: - Recencia (30 días) *0.3
            
            P-->>S: posts con score de relevancia
            
            S->>R: 7. SETEX community:personalized:feed:{userId} (TTL 120s)
            
            S-->>C: 8. 200 OK (posts ordenados por relevancia)
            C-->>U: 9. Mostrar feed personalizado
        end
    end